name: The Cubetastic Cube
description:
You play as a cube and you go flying down a path and can not stop. Don't hit anything or you die and have to restart. There are 10 levels to beat if you want to complete the game. It's not the best but its works, have fun!(also the music is LOUD so lowing the volume).

btw: this is my first game every made and every posted online :]

by: Blockhead Manic
